^Rovill.~, ^Sessa~, ^Crus.~, ^Misserini~, ^Vol.~, ^Dion.~, ^De
Rom.~, ^Fantoni~, ^Ed. Pad.~, ^Pezzana~, ^Sicca~, ^Quattro
Fior.~, ^Fosc.~, ^Witte~, ^Fanf.~, ecc.  Cos@i i commentatori:
^Buti~, ^Land.~, ^Vell.~, ^Dol.~, ^Dan.~, ^Vol.~, ^D'Aq.~,
^Vent.~, ^Lomb.~, ^Port.~, ^Pogg.~, ^Biag.~, ^Cost.~, ^Ces.~,
